### Created Files:

**`__tests__/services/permission/api/index.test.ts`** (144 lines)
- Tests for getPermissionApi and savePermissionApi
- Mocks @semparar/mf-app-user
```typescript
it('should call correct endpoint with account number in header', async () => {
  expect(api.get).toHaveBeenCalledWith('fintech/v1/rewardProgram/consult-permission', {
    headers: { codigoCliente: '12345678' },
  });
});
```

**`__tests__/services/permission/repository/index.test.ts`** (93 lines)
- Pure function tests for mapPermissionResponse
- Tests null/undefined handling
```typescript
it('should extract value from valid response', () => {
  const result = mapPermissionResponse(mockResponse);
  expect(result).toEqual({
    invoiceCashbackRedemption: { redeemedAtDate: '2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z' }
  });
});
```

**`__tests__/services/permission/services/index.test.ts`** (237 lines)
- Tests checkHasRedeemed and markAsRedeemed business logic
- Tests state transitions: IDLE → LOADING → SUCCESS/ERROR
